#summary Unresolved Turmites of 2 state and 2 colors.

= Introduction =

There are about 570 unresolved 2-state 2-color turmites listed below.  This is a subpage of EdPeggsBusyBeaverTurmiteChallenge.

==Rules==

These have all been run with about 1.6 billion steps. The exact number of iterations is unknown as the simulation stops when a certain size is reached. Some only ran for about 1 billion steps. Mark is still in the process of eliminating even more as a simulation of 6.4 billion steps is under way.
